structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.text: If any Commonwealth's or county attorney fails to take the steps required by KRS 69.040 or 69.240 within sixty (60) days after they could have been taken, he shall forfeit all right to any percent of the judgment whenever collected and paid into the State Treasury.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 130.
